OL,4,CTeacher smothered son, 2, before
OL,5,Ctaking own life
OL,7,FWarning: this article contains details
OL,8,Fof an upsetting nature
OL,10,FAn inquest has heard how an English
OL,11,Fteacher from North Staffordshire
OL,12,Fsmothered her two-year old son, before
OL,13,Ftaking her own life in a prison cell.
OL,15,FAyesha Henna Ali suffered a
OL,16,F"breakdown" and killed her child while
OL,17,Fhe was in bed.
OL,19,FAli who was 35, was a Keele University
OL,20,Fgraduate from Newcastle-under-Lyme,
OL,21,Fliving in Finland at the time.
