OL,4,CTeacher smothered son, 2, before
OL,5,Ctaking own life
OL,7,FAfter Adam's death, she video-called
OL,8,Fher mother, saying "I've done
OL,9,Fsomething terrible".
OL,11,FThe alarm was raised but Adam had
OL,12,Falready died when police got inside
OL,13,Fthe apartment near the Finnish capital
OL,14,Fof Helsinki, on 19th January 2020.
OL,16,FAyesha also had self-inflicted wounds.
OL,18,FNineteen days after killing her son,
OL,19,FAyesha was found hanged in her prison
OL,20,Fcell. She was confirmed dead in
OL,21,Fhospital on the 6th February 2020.
