OL,7,FThe inquest, held at Stoke Coroner's
OL,8,FCourt, heard Ayesha was described by
OL,9,Fher parents as a 'lively, kind and
OL,10,Fclever' woman, but her mental health
OL,11,Ftook a downward spiral in April 2019,
OL,12,Fafter the relationship with her
OL,13,Fhusband broke down.
OL,15,FShe had appointments with mental
OL,16,Fhealth critical care teams in April
OL,17,Fand May 2019, but seemed to be
OL,18,Fimproving by August 2019 and was
OL,19,Fdischarged.
