OL,4,CTeacher smothered son, 2, before
OL,5,Ctaking own life
OL,7,FShe then moved from Newcastle-under-
OL,8,FLyme, to Finland.
OL,10,F"I do not deserve to live"
OL,12,FAyesha wrote in her statement before
OL,13,Fkilling herself:
OL,15,F"I put my son in the bath around 7pm
OL,16,Fand I gave him some fruit and yoghurt
OL,17,Fbefore putting him in my bed.
OL,19,F"He didn't have his own room. He would
OL,20,Fhug me in the morning - it was the
OL,21,Fbest".
