OL,4,CTeacher smothered son, 2, before
OL,5,Ctaking own life
OL,7,FThe inquest heard Ayesha attempted to
OL,8,Fend her life in a prison cell while in
OL,9,Fcustody.
OL,11,FThe prison guard said he was not told
OL,12,Fby the police that Ayesha was
OL,13,Fsuicidal, but he immediately raised
OL,14,Fconcerns to the prison's psychiatric
OL,15,Fclinic.
OL,17,FAyesha was then left alone in the cell
OL,18,F- which had "white privacy paint" on
OL,19,Fthe windows to abide by Finnish laws -
OL,20,Ffor 20 to 30 minutes. She later died
OL,21,Ffrom severe brain injuries in hospital.
