OL,7,F"She loved her child and couldn't live
OL,8,Fone minute without him"
OL,10,FAyesha's heartbroken mother Safia said:
OL,12,F"We have nothing left now, I have lost
OL,13,Fmy only child and my only grandchild.
OL,14,FWe've lost our whole life.
OL,16,F"Ayesha had a Masters in Human Rights
OL,17,Fand wanted to help people. She was
OL,18,Fkind.J"She loved her child and
OL,19,Fcouldn't live one minute without him.
OL,20,FShe ... thought she was giving her
OL,21,Fchild peace.
